manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Product Description The multi-function doorbell adapter saves you the trouble of frequent battery replacementSpecial design and high quality materials ensure that the adapter is kept in low temperature to charge safely，Suitable for various doorbell videos and thermostats

Continuously Charging It can be continuously Power supply your device without worry about taking off the doorbells/ thermostats and low battery, which is time-saving and effort-saving. For Doorbells 1.Keep adapter unplugged. 2.Install wires from 24 volt adapter into the terminals for your doorbell unit (Simply attach the two exposed copper wires to the doorbell and tighten the screws, regardless of positive or negative polarity) 3.Plug adapter into outlet. 4.Power up and verify your doorbell is receiving necessary power using the accompanying application. 1.Cut off the power of circuit breaker. 2.Install the wire from your 24 volt adapter to the “C” terminal and the other wire to the “RC” terminal. You need to use included jumper and connect from “RH” to “RC” terminals，if HVAC system has a cooling. 3.Plug the power adapter into the socket and turn on the power of the circuit breaker. Install the panel on the thermostat.
